data.description: Discover your dream home in Enterprise, South West Las Vegas! This unique 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom property boasts 3584 sq ft of living space, an oversized two-car garage, RV Parking and a rare FULL SIZE basement with brand new windows —all set on a spacious half-acre lot in a non-HOA community. The recently remodeled open floor plan offers ample room for comfort and style, while the unfinished backyard serves as a blank canvas for endless possibilities! Located in the coveted Enterprise area, you're just a short drive from the Raiders Stadium, South Las Vegas Strip, Harry Reid International Airport and all the incredible amenities Las Vegas has to offer! Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a versatile and spacious home in one of the city's most sought-after neighborhoods!
